title: Jaal: The Trap
subTitle: Ajay, a commando, is forced to kidnap Anita, the home minister's daughter, to free his girlfriend Neha from the clutches of terrorists. In the process, he uncovers a shocking revelation.

title: Insan
subTitle: Ajit Rathod, a grieving policeman, vows to catch his wife's killer, terrorist Azhar Khan. He pursues Azhar with single-minded focus, overcoming all hurdles.
